# Supabase DB Schema (mínimo) — MVP10

## Tablas existentes usadas
- dts_assessments
- dts_criteria
- dts_responses
- dts_assessment_scores
- dts_dimension_scores
- dts_chat_messages

## Nueva tabla: dts_initiatives (MVP)
Campos mínimos:
- id uuid pk default gen_random_uuid()
- assessment_id uuid (fk dts_assessments)
- criterion_code text  (ej "6.1.1")
- initiative_code text unique per assessment (ej "6.1.1.A")
- type text check in ('Quick Win','Base estructural','Transformacional','Mantenimiento')
- category text check in ('BASE','AMPLIFIER','MAINTENANCE')
- title text
- description text null
- owner_role text
- status text check in ('pending','in_progress','blocked','done') default 'pending'
- due_date date null
- evidence_note text null
- evidence_url text null
- last_update_at timestamptz null

Engines:
- effort_base int
- effort_final int
- weeks_min int
- weeks_max int
- impact_hours_base int
- impact_hours_final int
- impact_eur_min numeric null
- impact_eur_max numeric null

Dependencies:
- dependencies text[] default '{}'

## Nueva tabla: dts_roadmap_items (opcional)
- assessment_id uuid
- initiative_code text
- quarter text ('Q1','Q2','Q3')
- order_in_quarter int
- created_at, updated_at

## Nueva tabla: dts_alerts (opcional)
- assessment_id uuid
- type text
- message text
- severity int (1..3)
- created_at
